'Mathematics are now become a popular Study, and make a part of the education of almost every Gentleman.'
</p><p>
Thus Stone began the preface to his translation of Nicolas Bion's master-work over two hundred years ago, and thus today, but loss neatly, speak our Ministers of Eductaion, our Commissions, our Pundits and our Authorities.
</p><p>
Nicolas Bion...
